_sText:
City with many buildings which are fully accesible. 2 Bombsites great face to face combat. Hope you all enjoy...

Features: 2 Bombsites, 3 Ways to attack. Great Sniper Spots, 2 Secret areas (1 admin accesible only(18+yrsold)) Realistic.

Author: GabrielPapaK

Time: 30 Hours, due to many errors with the map...


Install:
Extract the map file (de_guerilla_city_gpk.bsp), also the  (de_guerilla_city_gpk.bsp.bak) and the navigation file (many_houses_wcs.nav) to your Counter-Strike maps folder (Usually located here:C:\Program Files\steam\steamapps\***YOURNAMEHERE***\counter-strike source\cstrike\maps).
